{"tid":908453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有睇西九補選論壇嘅可唔可以入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-11-19T14:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T18:10:37.000Z","uid":179824,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1a08f78f17fb8648f383bfe1a89ae9b2fe3e28ea","tid":908453,"uid":179824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"先利申我知道自己關注得政事唔夠多 呢排終於忙完會努力惡補 身邊冇人關注所以上嚟問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係九龍西區選民 啱啱滿歲數第一次投票<br />\n今日睇完港台個西九區補選<br />\n未睇之前本身已經好奇點解會出民主派兩大元老 係咪有咩誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後睇馮檢基基哥係咁不滿李卓人 似乎有內亂<br />\n咁我於是上網睇翻做下research <br />\n發現啲人一時又傳基哥係建制B隊 一時又話李卓人係欽點空降九龍西<br />\n泛民主派內亂到我依家分唔清到底投指定候選人李卓人定係好似眾叛親離嘅基哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺忽視只會係咁講美孚新邨無咩料到嘅曾麗文嘅前提下，唔想「欣為你」當選應該投邊個有勝算？<br />\n到底基哥真係變節定只係真心膠？<br />\n<br />\n真心求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ba4bbeed8d536faf91af46d3c63b344df1d854","tid":908453,"uid":179824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔想鳩投但係真係睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef55e8a9f3dd92b2dd0d514fb7b32cccb9add910","tid":908453,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"係變節又點真心膠又點<br />\n點選都係咖哩味屎 屎味咖哩"},{"pid":"6b9279108e35abc6e112b373e0acfa39580a0bcd","tid":908453,"uid":56147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"update 你<br />\n照定義黎立法會係做呢D<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/intro/about_lc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fintro%2Fabout_lc.htm&d=ayxGCzeFtYLQTdJ4vPfzYywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ebe16f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/intro/about_lc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n但係有班唔係靠選既功能組別垃圾係度污染個立法會<br />\n拎住百幾萬票既果班 係立法會入面唔夠廿幾萬票果班投票<br />\n<br />\n所以而家立法會只係一個千幾萬budget 既位 <br />\n選黎係為左個千幾萬   無其他意義"},{"pid":"2bdcc60f73719a51912b07c0ece7c474110252df","tid":908453,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"投李卓仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9ae46099ea44e9a5934f59d9f60c579d183927","tid":908453,"uid":179824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef55e8a9f3dd92b2dd0d514fb7b32cccb9add910","tid":908453,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"係變節又點真心膠又點<br />\n點選都係咖哩味屎 屎味咖哩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁有冇lesser evil 嘅說法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係唔想投一個陳凱欣入去 真係屎味嘅屎"},{"pid":"f5744cf2ccc5fa7ae91d6c978a89692e237ddbd0","tid":908453,"uid":179824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6b9279108e35abc6e112b373e0acfa39580a0bcd","tid":908453,"uid":56147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"update 你<br />\n照定義黎立法會係做呢D<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/intro/about_lc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fintro%2Fabout_lc.htm&d=ayxGCzeFtYLQTdJ4vPfzYywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ebe16f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/intro/about_lc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n但係有班唔係靠選既功能組別垃圾係度污染個立法會<br />\n拎住百幾萬票既果班 係立法會入面唔夠廿幾萬票果班投票<br />\n<br />\n所以而家立法會只係一個千幾萬budget 既位 <br />\n選黎係為左個千幾萬   無其他意義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"雖然建制已經過半數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我唔知點解覺得呢票始終都係